snippet.title: FINAL FURY | Gameplay Trailer | Meta Quest & Steam VR
snippet.description:
Sign up to play first at: https://finalfuryvr.com/?ref=myt

Enter a new era of combat in FINAL FURY, a groundbreaking VR fighting game inspired by the golden age of arcade fighters. Duke it out in epic head-to-head matches like never before with immersive visuals, innovative controls, and fast-paced gameplay tailored for newcomers and veterans alike. 

Wishlist on Steam today at: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1782760/FINAL_FURY/

Open Beta coming early 2024 to Meta Quest 2, Meta Quest 3 and Meta Quest Pro.

#MetaQuest #Quest3 #VRGaming #FGC
